OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with showers. These
OL,7,Fshowers will die from late evening as
OL,8,Fclear spells spread west, leading to a
OL,9,Ffrosty end to the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA frosty, dry and sunny start
OL,12,Fto the day will be followed by
OL,13,Fbuilding cloud during the morning and
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain spreading north
OL,15,Ftowards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
